6. Configuration modification 

Clone the following git repository
https://git.lab14.example.com/git/modconf.git
Perform the following tasks
--> edit your configuration with following changes
		--> Disable fact gathering permanently
		--> Simultaneously ansible should reach 40 hosts
--> Once the modification is done, commit and push updated configuration to the remote repository

Answer:


	#cd /home/admin/git-repos/
	#git clone <git repo>
	#cd fork-project
	#vim ansible.cfg
	
	[defaults]
	inventory=inventory
	remote_user=admin
	forks=40
	gathering=explicit

	[privilege_escalation]
	become=True
	become_method=sudo
	become_user=root
	become_ask_pass=False

# git add .
# git commit -m 'coomit name'
# git push
# cd ..
